{"tid":2414050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"緬甸頭部中槍女示威者今早正式宣告死亡","createTime":"2021-02-19T06:34:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T13:09:40.000Z","uid":153600,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5475e6572c3e11d51babd00668688d54ce97287e","tid":2414050,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T06:34:20.000Z","msg":"早前緬甸警方動用武力，驅散抗議政變嘅示威者，其中一名20歲嘅女仔Mya Thwate Thwate Khaing喺首都奈比多被子彈擊中頭部，《路透社》曾報導，一名不願具名嘅醫生講，女子頭部受傷，X光照片顯示有實彈卡喺佢嘅頭部，並且話「她還沒死，在加護病房，但100%確定會死」。<br />\n<br />\n該名少女今早正式宣告死亡，係首名喺抗爭中喪生嘅示威者。Mya Thwate Thwate Khaing喺入院之後一直陷於腦死亡狀態，外媒報道稱，家屬喺四日前已同意拔除少女嘅維生支援，但被軍方阻止，終延至星期五，喺當地時間早上11時15分醫生宣告死亡。<br />\n<br />\nRIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5328feefecf38ab0abd98dae5eae4bc38d70e50","tid":2414050,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T06:36:50.000Z","msg":"RIP......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"514f9be141fbe108c336659a5a27ef1ca08b59da","tid":2414050,"uid":163447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T06:38:18.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"8711fd3d3265bb856a023cac85da71757645615b","tid":2414050,"uid":155095,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T06:38:32.000Z","msg":"兇手<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QBHPdnt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQBHPdnt.jpg&h=180dc7af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a88b8bb10fdd1fc6b733a630e75216bbdebf6789","tid":2414050,"u